---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---
<Layout title="EICR Testing | Electrical Safety Certificates | MET Electrical" description="Professional EICR testing in Somerset. Landlord compliance, electrical safety certificates, and comprehensive inspections by qualified electricians.">
  <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-yellow text-sm font-medium mb-4">
        <Icon name="tabler:certificate" class="w-5 h-5" />
        ELECTRICAL SAFETY TESTING
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">EICR Testing & Certification</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/70 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Electrical Installation Condition Reports for landlords and homeowners. Professional inspections ensuring your property meets current safety standards.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Quick Facts -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
        <Icon name="tabler:clock" class="w-12 h-12 text-brand-yellow mx-auto mb-3" />
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Same-Day Reports</h3>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Fast turnaround for urgent landlord requirements</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
        <Icon name="tabler:shield-check" class="w-12 h-12 text-brand-yellow mx-auto mb-3" />
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Landlord Compliance</h3>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Meet the 5-year testing requirement for rental properties</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
        <Icon name="tabler:award" class="w-12 h-12 text-brand-yellow mx-auto mb-3" />
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Qualified Inspector</h3>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">18th Edition qualified, NAPIT registered electrician</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">What is an EICR?</h2>
          <p class="text-white/80 mb-4">An Electrical Installation Condition Report (EICR) is a comprehensive inspection of your property's electrical systems. It identifies any defects, deterioration, or potential safety issues with your wiring, sockets, switches, and consumer unit.</p>
          <p class="text-white/80">The inspection covers the condition of electrical installations against the current version of the BS 7671 wiring regulations (18th Edition).</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Who Needs an EICR?</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Icon name="tabler:home" class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-yellow mt-1 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Landlords (Legal Requirement)</h3>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Private rental properties must have a valid EICR renewed every 5 years, or upon change of tenancy if more than 5 years old.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Icon name="tabler:users" class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-yellow mt-1 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Homeowners</h3>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Recommended every 10 years for owner-occupied homes, or when buying/selling a property.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <Icon name="tabler:building" class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-yellow mt-1 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Businesses</h3>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Commercial properties should be tested every 5 years, or every 3 years for high-risk environments.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our EICR Process</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-semibold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium">Visual Inspection</h4>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Checking visible electrical equipment for obvious defects</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-semibold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">2</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium">Testing & Measurements</h4>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Using calibrated test equipment to check circuits and safety devices</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-semibold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">3</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium">Documentation</h4>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Detailed report with findings, observations, and recommendations</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-full w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-semibold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">4</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium">Certification</h4>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Official EICR certificate if installation is satisfactory</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-8 space-y-6">
        <!-- Quick Quote -->
        <div class="bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg p-6 border border-brand-blue/20">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Get Your EICR Quote</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-4 text-sm">Fast, professional EICR testing across Somerset. Same-day service available.</p>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <a href="tel:07464336661" class="block w-full btn-primary text-center">Call 07464 336661</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="block w-full btn-secondary text-center">Request Quote</a>
            <a href="https://wa.me/447464336661?text=Hi%2C%20I%20need%20an%20EICR%20test" class="block w-full btn bg-green-600 text-white hover:bg-green-500 text-center">
              <Icon name="tabler:brand-whatsapp" class="w-4 h-4 mr-1" /> WhatsApp
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Key Points -->
        <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 border border-white/10">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-yellow" />
            What You Get
          </h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-white/80">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow flex-shrink-0"></span>
              Comprehensive electrical safety inspection
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow flex-shrink-0"></span>
              Detailed written report with photos
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow flex-shrink-0"></span>
              Official EICR certificate (if satisfactory)
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow flex-shrink-0"></span>
              Priority repair recommendations
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow flex-shrink-0"></span>
              Same-day service available
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Service Area -->
        <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 border border-white/10">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Icon name="tabler:map-pin" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-yellow" />
            Service Area
          </h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/70 mb-3">Based in Shepton Mallet, serving:</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-white/60 space-y-1">
            <li>• Taunton & surrounding areas</li>
            <li>• Yeovil & South Somerset</li>
            <li>• Bridgwater & Sedgemoor</li>
            <li>• Frome & Mendip areas</li>
            <li>• Wells & Glastonbury</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">How long does an EICR take?</h4>
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Typically 2-4 hours depending on the size and complexity of the property. Larger properties may take longer.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">What happens if my EICR fails?</h4>
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">We'll provide a detailed report of any issues found. Many problems can be fixed on the same day, allowing for re-certification.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">Do you provide same-day certificates?</h4>
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Yes, if the installation passes inspection, certificates are typically provided on the same day as the testing.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">What areas do you cover?</h4>
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">We cover all of Somerset including Taunton, Yeovil, Bridgwater, Frome, Wells, Glastonbury and surrounding areas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Back to Services -->
    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-yellow hover:text-white transition">
        <Icon name="tabler:arrow-left" class="w-4 h-4" />
        Back to All Services
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>